  <name>Roll-It</name>
  <summary>Roll the dice</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Roll-It simulates the results of rolling a die.</p>
    <p>By default, the maximum possible roll is six, as six-sided dice are the most common. However, the user can set the maximum amount to any number between one and one-hundred.</p>
  </description>
